3.6. Multivariate Statistical Analysis of Chemical Composition
Hierarchical cluster analysis was carried out to organize and cluster the essential oils according to
their main volatile constituents. Complete linkage and absolute correlation coefﬁcient distance was
chosen to determine similarity. Agglomerative hierarchical clustering was utilized for clustering the
essential oils. The MINITAB 14.0 software was used to statistically analyze all data.
